2. Environmental Controls
HVAC (Heating, Ventilation, Air Conditioning)

Fire suppression systems

Water leak detectors

Dust filters

Raised floors

These protect against environmental threats.

3. Hardware Protection
Rack enclosures

Lockable server cabinets

Tamper-proof devices

Alarm systems

4. Power Supply Protection
Protects against deviations in power quality (noted in your file):

UPS systems

Backup generators

Surge suppressors

